title: Girl with Binoculars
description: An illustration of a girl wearing a bright pink hoodie and blue pants, looking through a pair of binoculars. She has long dark hair tied back in a ponytail and is focused on something in the distance.

title: Cranes in Flight
description: An illustration of four cranes flying in a V formation. The cranes are depicted with white bodies, black wing tips, and red crowns on their heads. The background is plain white, emphasizing the graceful movement of the birds.
